{"tid":731480,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺香港新樓開價算有良心？","createTime":"2018-07-06T08:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T12:45:00.000Z","uid":174530,"like":22,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cadd02c5dc35142fd0e7f0435794a4f06ab970e0","tid":731480,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"宜家講緊少極每個月升緊1-2%，一年正常都有40%升幅<br />\n但新樓仲係開緊2萬到4萬蚊一呎<br />\n發展商都承受住好大既風險<br />\n其實賺少左好多<br />\n<br />\n加上，發展商都驚唔係人人買到樓，就整200呎既單位<br />\n左度右度幫你間屋整到最精緻<br />\n等你地入場費唔洗太貴，500萬200呎非常好<br />\n<br />\n生命係無價，樓係永遠<br />\n樓奴講得好岩，話貴又唱淡果d係失敗者，係社會上既寄生蟲<br />\n過幾年，社會既正常人只會人人有層樓，人人有二千萬。"},{"pid":"efd40f639d8b4ae3d42ee3ad057138e75e826c30","tid":731480,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22b25a694eccdf18adc870f88b797f06117b7466","tid":731480,"uid":174530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efd40f639d8b4ae3d42ee3ad057138e75e826c30","tid":731480,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"岩呀，蝕左成80%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e220591c760b04662fd92137d462849021f9f7b","tid":731480,"uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:23:00.000Z","msg":"時日無多，散貨要緊。"},{"pid":"433c044f68a1c7b73c6a22e8719e2e0aa0df633d","tid":731480,"uid":153984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efd40f639d8b4ae3d42ee3ad057138e75e826c30","tid":731480,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"發展商：我都賺夠啦 係時候俾其他人賺吓"},{"pid":"6d4a2151ce2d623da8ed6ce49c60ee6fed90268b","tid":731480,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:24:17.000Z","msg":"20000一呎基本上係半賣半送啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2415c0389fe431b68a74f490fac208fa616442","tid":731480,"uid":12609,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"唔係發展商起咁多樓，香港人一早訓街<br />\n仲要賣得20000一呎咁平，簡直係良心企業<br />\n香港人應該感恩"},{"pid":"4c661c6437c26b7dd607406841a1f41f7c4a3d73","tid":731480,"uid":85564,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"根本個樓價就冇問題<br />\n<br />\n其他國家大城市都係咁上下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買唔起係你廢 <br />\n<br />\n唔識投機 淨係識腳踏實地鳩下鳩下<br />\n<br />\n你怨天怨地不如諗下辦法與天鬥與地鬥<br />\n<br />\n真係冇能力嘅話 訓街係理所當然<br />\n<br />\n鬼叫你咁撚廢呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:曲"},{"pid":"088f4ceaf05f611d7fecce3dde3f2cdccc73475a","tid":731480,"uid":192190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:20:46.000Z","msg":"係呀, 發展商唔係為賺錢 只求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5441028ab64e2efca6a60622017fb5f560cfdf6","tid":731480,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"係丫，一買即賺"},{"pid":"a6a19e6aa017ef56d1b3c4c4c4d3354b289f12ee","tid":731480,"uid":6562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"係呀 有良心到唔好意思幫趁佢 <br />\n真係唔覺佢係想做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5f6205e887f02760e5e30c5e272df74e4ea9a8","tid":731480,"uid":99766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"係呀，賺夠啦，但求打個和算"},{"pid":"d67c5749f1b5084e152effce81d1bddf66659374","tid":731480,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6a19e6aa017ef56d1b3c4c4c4d3354b289f12ee","tid":731480,"uid":6562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"係呀 有良心到唔好意思幫趁佢 <br />\n真係唔覺佢係想做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply